arrival_location.prompt_template:
The adventuring party was at this location:

Location: {previous_location_name}
Description: {previous_location_description}

They chose to take this path onward:

Path: {path_name}
Description: {path_description}

Generate the location the party arrives at after taking this path. It should make sense as somewhere this path could lead, but it may surprise the party - the path only sometimes hints at its destination.

Respond with valid JSON in this exact format:
{{"name": "Location Name", "description": "1-2 sentence description of what the party sees, hears, and feels in this new location. Make it atmospheric and immersive."}}

